name: 8 Row Kinzie 3000 Planter
description: Bring to you the Kinze 8/15 3000 series planter. This model comes with many variations such as being able to select no fertilizer to liquid fertilizer to dry fertilizer. Also includes the function to plant directly into unworked ground (no-til operation) Hope you enjoy this mod. Blake Chamness made this mod for fs19 and has given me full permission to release it in fs22. Also credit goes out to RedRock's Shop and to Scooter Workbench for all the added help to make this possible. Hope you all enjoy!
